name: Reminder No.1
description: Reminder No.1 Special mystical desktop device (50/50) helps keep in mind that our planet is very beautiful and very fragile, so we should care about her and love her like a Mother. The whale is guard and he is on duty always. You can use Reminder as screensaver, it gives relaxing and meditative state. The soundtrack is also gentle. Please enjoy! Love and peace to everyone!
